title: 我的世界1.7.10一进入存档就闪退怎么办
author: 王子杰拉尔
txt_content:
这几天老出问题，难道是我装了win10还是mod问题啊。昨天又新创建了一个生存玩，共37mod，无材质光影，今天走了几步就闪退了，然后重登，每次刚进入地图半秒不到就出现正在关闭内置服务端，然后闪退，然后我删了TMI修改器后就好了，玩了一个小时又无限闪退了，这怎么办啊，崩溃日志是不是叫  hmcmc  啊，我就看了四行去百度翻译了下
[23:31:33] [Client thread/WARN] [levelup]: Mod levelup is missing the required element 'version' and a version.properties file could not be found. Falling back to metadata version 0.6
[23:31:33] [Client thread/WARN] [DamageIndicatorsMod]: Mod DamageIndicatorsMod is missing the required element 'version' and a version.properties file could not be found. Falling back to metadata version 3.2.0
[23:31:33] [Client thread/WARN] [lmmx]: Mod lmmx is missing the required element 'version' and no fallback can be found. Substituting '1.0'.
[23:31:33] [Client thread/WARN] [zabuton]: Mod zabuton is missing the required element 'version' and no fallback can be found. Substituting '1.0'.
翻译结果
[ 23:31:33 ] [客户] [级别]线/警告：MOD LevelUp缺少必需的元素“版本”和version.properties文件无法找到。返回元数据版本0.6[23:31:33] [Client thread/WARN] [DamageIndicatorsMod]: Mod DamageIndicatorsMod is missing the required element 'version' and a version.properties file could not be found. Falling back to metadata version 3.2.0[ 23:31:33 ] [客户端线程/警告] [ damageindicatorsmod ]：国防部damageindicatorsmod缺少必需的元素“版本”和version.properties文件无法找到。落回元数据3.2.0版本[23:31:33] [Client thread/WARN] [lmmx]: Mod lmmx is missing the required element 'version' and no fallback can be found. Substituting '1.0'.[ 23:31:33 ] [客户端线程/警告] [ lmmx ]：国防部lmmx缺少必需的元素“版本”，没有退路可发现。代以“1”。[23:31:33] [Client thread/WARN] [zabuton]: Mod zabuton is missing the required element 'version' and no fallback can be found. Substituting '1.0'.[ 23:31:33 ] [客户端线程/警告] [拜壂]：MOD拜壂缺少必需的元素“版本”，没有退路可发现。代以“1”。
